title: Inspiration from Olympic champion Kikkan Randall plus hummingbirds and mini ski jumps from Lausanne 2020
description: Five-time Olympian cross-country skier and cancer survivor Kikkan Randall spoke at the Chat with Champions event about how to combat negative thoughts. Plus, a last question with figure skater with figure skater Kate Wang.
